00:09:33.860 --> 00:09:40.980
initiative to be with them, comfort them, show them love in such a difficult time. Well, brothers,

00:09:40.980 --> 00:09:48.980
what do we learn from all of this? We are in a time of increased stress, of increased anxiety.

00:09:49.860 --> 00:09:58.340
We all have the power to help others through acts of kindness and deeds of goodness that show

00:09:58.340 --> 00:10:07.220
generosity and love. Let's be motivated by our good conscience to do those good and kind and

00:10:07.220 --> 00:10:12.659
generous things that really show that we're imitators of our Heavenly Father, Jehovah.

00:10:13.379 --> 00:10:20.500
And as we do, we're going to find that our stress will be relieved. And at the same time,

00:10:20.500 --> 00:10:28.580
